4. 

aqi$ <- str_replace_all(aqi$, "[]", "") # 
aqi$PM2.5 <- str_replace_all(aqi$PM2.5, "[g/m|g/m]", "") # 
aqi$PM10 <- str_replace_all(aqi$PM10, "[g/m|g/m]", "")
aqi$ <- str_replace_all(aqi$, "[]", "NA") 
aqi$AQI <- parse_double(aqi$AQI, na = "NA") # 

aqi$PM2.5 <- parse_number(aqi$PM2.5, na = "NA") # 
aqi$PM10 <- parse_number(aqi$PM10, na = "NA")

aqi$ <- parse_factor(aqi$, na = "NA") # 
level <- c("", "", "", "", "")
aqi$ <- parse_factor(aqi$, levels = level, na = "NA") 
aqi <- rename(aqi, PM2.5 = PM2.5, PM10 = PM10)
# 6
head(aqi)
